web.xml for tomcat 
jsp and servlet



web.xml is under WEB-INF directory 

it includes servlet info 

ex: 
<servlet> 
<servlet-name>Chapter1 Servlet</servlet-name> 
<servlet-class>Ch1Servlet</servlet-class> 
</servlet> 

<servlet-mapping> 
<servlet-name>Chapter1 Servlet</servlet-name> 
<url-pattern>/Serv1</url-pattern> 
</servlet-mapping> 

Ch1Servlet is java class name 
Serv1 is URL request path, it will trigger java class Ch1Servlet to run 